title: #92Noon At TCO/Florio/Edwards & Filippo Presser/Musburger
description: Training camp may be over but PA & Nordo are at #TCO! Wobby joins them for a minute. Adrian Peterson has joined the WA Redskins. Mike Florio lets us know what the rules really are. A 'would you rather' scenario with Nordo. Press conference with Vikings defensive coordinator, George Edwards, and later offensive coordinator, John DeFilippo. Broadcasting legend, Brent Musburger, calls in.
